			<p style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;<b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">LEI N.&ordm; 15.175, DE 28.06.12 (D.O. 11.07.12)</span></b></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 450px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Define regras espec&iacute;ficas para a implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o do disposto na lei federal n&ordm;. 12.527, de 18 de novembro de 2011, no &acirc;mbito da administra&ccedil;&atilde;o p&uacute;blica do Estado do Cear&aacute;, e d&aacute; outras provid&ecirc;ncias.&nbsp;</span></b></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 225pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span></b></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;">O GOVERNADOR DO ESTADO DO CEAR&Aacute;.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;">FA&Ccedil;O SABER QUE A ASSEMBLEIA LEGISLATIVA DECRETOU E EU SANCIONO A SEGUINTE LEI:</span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 2cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span></b></span></p>
<p style="margin-left: 2cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span></b></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">CAP&Iacute;TULO I</span></b></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">DISPOSI&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES GERAIS</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 1</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&ordm; Esta Lei define regras espec&iacute;ficas a serem observadas pelos poderes e &oacute;rg&atilde;os da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica do Estado do Cear&aacute;, com o fim de assegurar a implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o do disposto na Lei Federal n&ordm;. 12.527, de 18 de novembro de 2011, que regula o acesso a informa&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico. <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Subordinam-se ao regime desta Lei:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- os &oacute;rg&atilde;os p&uacute;blicos integrantes da administra&ccedil;&atilde;o direta dos Poderes Executivo, Legislativo, incluindo as Cortes de Contas, Judici&aacute;rio e do Minist&eacute;rio P&uacute;blico Estadual;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- as autarquias, as funda&ccedil;&otilde;es p&uacute;blicas, as empresas p&uacute;blicas, as sociedades de economia mista e demais entidades controladas direta ou indiretamente pelo Estado do Cear&aacute;.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 2</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&ordm; Aplicam-se as disposi&ccedil;&otilde;es desta Lei, no que couber, &agrave;s entidades privadas sem fins lucrativos que recebam, para realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de a&ccedil;&otilde;es de interesse p&uacute;blico, recursos p&uacute;blicos mediante contrato de gest&atilde;o, termo de parceria, conv&ecirc;nios, acordo, ajustes ou outros instrumentos cong&ecirc;neres.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico. <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A publicidade, a que est&atilde;o submetidas &agrave;s entidades citadas no caput, refere-se &agrave; parcela dos recursos p&uacute;blicos recebidos e &agrave; sua destina&ccedil;&atilde;o, sem preju&iacute;zo das presta&ccedil;&otilde;es de contas a que estejam legalmente obrigadas.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 3&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Para os efeitos desta Lei, considera-se:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I -</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o de Interesse P&uacute;blico: toda aquela informa&ccedil;&atilde;o que n&atilde;o &eacute; de car&aacute;ter pessoal ou classificada como sigilosa;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II -</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o Sigilosa: <b><span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></b></span>aquela submetida temporariamente &agrave; restri&ccedil;&atilde;o de acesso p&uacute;blico em raz&atilde;o de sua imprescindibilidade para a seguran&ccedil;a da sociedade e do Estado, podendo ser classificada em Reservada, Secreta e Ultrassecreta:</span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">a) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o Reservada: as que ficam sob sigilo durante o prazo de 5 (cinco) anos e no caso do Estado, as que puderem colocar em risco a seguran&ccedil;a dos Chefes de Poderes, inclusive Cortes de Contas e Minist&eacute;rio P&uacute;blico;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">b) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o Secreta: as que ficam sob sigilo durante o prazo de 15 (cinco) anos;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">c)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o Ultrassecreta: as que ficam sob sigilo durante o prazo de 25 (vinte e cinco) anos;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III -</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o Pessoal: aquela relacionada &agrave; pessoa natural identificada ou identific&aacute;vel.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">CAP&Iacute;TULO II</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">DO SISTEMA ESTADUAL DE ACESSO &Agrave; INFORMA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 1cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 4&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Fica criado o Sistema Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, composto pelo Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o e pelos Comit&ecirc;s Gestores de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">. No Poder Executivo Estadual, integram ainda o Sistema de que trata o caput, Comit&ecirc;s Setoriais de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 5&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Fica criado o Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, integrado por servidores designados pelos Chefes dos seguintes Poderes e &Oacute;rg&atilde;os:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- Poder Executivo;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- Poder Legislativo;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- Poder Judici&aacute;rio;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- Minist&eacute;rio P&uacute;blico;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">V</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- Tribunal de Contas do Estado do Cear&aacute;;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VI</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- Tribunal de Contas dos Munic&iacute;pios.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O Conselho previsto no caput decidir&aacute; sobre o tratamento e a classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sigilosas e ter&aacute; compet&ecirc;ncia para:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">a)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">requisitar do Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, esclarecimento ou conte&uacute;do, parcial ou integral da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o classificada como ultrassecreta e secreta;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">b)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">rever a classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ultrassecretas ou secretas, de of&iacute;cio ou mediante provoca&ccedil;&atilde;o de pessoa interessada;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">c) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">prorrogar o prazo de sigilo de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o classificada como ultrassecreta, sempre por prazo determinado, enquanto o seu acesso ou divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o puder ocasionar amea&ccedil;a &agrave; seguran&ccedil;a da sociedade ou do Estado, observado o prazo previsto no &sect; 1&ordm;, inciso I do art. 23;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">d)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">apreciar em &uacute;ltima inst&acirc;ncia administrativa os recursos interpostos por negativa dos Comit&ecirc;s Gestores de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&ordm; O prazo referido na al&iacute;nea &ldquo;c&rdquo; do &sect;1&ordm; &eacute; limitado a uma &uacute;nica renova&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A revis&atilde;o de of&iacute;cio a que se refere a al&iacute;nea &ldquo;b&rdquo; do &sect;1&ordm; dever&aacute; ocorrer, no m&aacute;ximo, a cada 4 (quatro) anos, ap&oacute;s a reavalia&ccedil;&atilde;o prevista no art. 7&ordm;, quando se tratar de documentos ultrassecretos ou secretos.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;4&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A n&atilde;o delibera&ccedil;&atilde;o sobre a revis&atilde;o pelo Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o nos prazos previstos no par&aacute;grafo anterior implicar&aacute; a desclassifica&ccedil;&atilde;o autom&aacute;tica das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;5&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Regulamento dispor&aacute; sobre a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e funcionamento do Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, observado o mandato de 2 (dois) anos para seus integrantes e demais disposi&ccedil;&otilde;es desta Lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 6&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Fica criado nos Poderes e &Oacute;rg&atilde;os de que trata o artigo anterior, o Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, com a finalidade de deliberar sobre a classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sigilosas e apreciar os recursos interpostos, observado o disposto nos arts. 16 e 17 desta Lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">No &acirc;mbito do Poder Executivo Estadual, o Comit&ecirc; de que trata o caput deste artigo ser&aacute; coordenado pela Controladoria e Ouvidoria Geral do Estado e ter&aacute; a seguinte composi&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">a)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Gabinete do Governador;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">b) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Casa Civil;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">c) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Procuradoria Geral do Estado;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">d) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Controladoria e Ouvidoria Geral do Estado;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">e)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Casa Militar;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">f) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Secretaria da Fazenda;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">g)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Secretaria do Planejamento e Gest&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Os demais Poderes e &Oacute;rg&atilde;os citados nos incisos II a VI, do art. 5&ordm; desta Lei definir&atilde;o, por ato pr&oacute;prio, a composi&ccedil;&atilde;o de seus Comit&ecirc;s Gestores de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 7&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Os Comit&ecirc;s Gestores de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o dever&atilde;o proceder &agrave; reavalia&ccedil;&atilde;o das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es classificadas como ultrassecretas e secretas no prazo m&aacute;ximo de 2 (dois) anos, contado do termo inicial de vig&ecirc;ncia desta Lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A restri&ccedil;&atilde;o de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&otilde;es, em raz&atilde;o da reavalia&ccedil;&atilde;o prevista no caput, dever&aacute; observar os prazos e condi&ccedil;&otilde;es previstos nesta Lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">No &acirc;mbito da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica Estadual, a reavalia&ccedil;&atilde;o prevista no caput poder&aacute; ser revista, a qualquer tempo, pelo Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, observados os termos desta Lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Enquanto n&atilde;o transcorrido o prazo de reavalia&ccedil;&atilde;o previsto no caput, ser&aacute; mantida a classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;4&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">As informa&ccedil;&otilde;es classificadas como secretas e ultrassecretas n&atilde;o reavaliadas no prazo previsto no caput ser&atilde;o consideradas, automaticamente, de acesso p&uacute;blico.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;5&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Regulamento dispor&aacute; sobre a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e funcionamento do Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 8&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Ficam criados nos &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades do Poder Executivo Estadual, os Comit&ecirc;s Setoriais de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, com a finalidade de assegurar o acesso imediato &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o dispon&iacute;vel e propor ao Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, a classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es no seu &acirc;mbito de atua&ccedil;&atilde;o, com a seguinte composi&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">a) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">titular do &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade ou autoridade com subordina&ccedil;&atilde;o imediata;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">b)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Assessor de Desenvolvimento Institucional ou cargo equivalente;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">c)</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Ouvidor Setorial;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">d) <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Respons&aacute;vel pelo Servi&ccedil;o de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ao Cidad&atilde;o;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O Comit&ecirc; de que trata o caput exercer&aacute; as seguintes atribui&ccedil;&otilde;es:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- assegurar o cumprimento das normas relativas ao acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, de forma eficiente e adequada aos objetivos desta Lei;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- monitorar a implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o do disposto nesta Lei e apresentar, ao Comit&ecirc; Gestor, relat&oacute;rios peri&oacute;dicos sobre o seu cumprimento;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- recomendar as medidas indispens&aacute;veis &agrave; implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o e ao aperfei&ccedil;oamento das normas e procedimentos necess&aacute;rios ao correto cumprimento do disposto nesta Lei;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- orientar as respectivas unidades no que se refere ao cumprimento do disposto nesta Lei e seus regulamentos.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A cria&ccedil;&atilde;o do Comit&ecirc;, de que trata o caput, fica facultada para o Poder Legislativo, Poder Judici&aacute;rio, Minist&eacute;rio P&uacute;blico, Tribunal de Contas do Estado do Cear&aacute; e Tribunal de Contas dos Munic&iacute;pios.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Regulamento dispor&aacute; sobre a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e funcionamento do Comit&ecirc; Setorial de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 9&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Ficam criados nos &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades, os Servi&ccedil;os de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ao Cidad&atilde;o, instalados em &aacute;reas de f&aacute;cil acesso ao p&uacute;blico, para:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">-&nbsp; atender e orientar o p&uacute;blico quanto ao acesso a informa&ccedil;&otilde;es;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">-&nbsp; informar sobre a tramita&ccedil;&atilde;o de documentos nas suas respectivas unidades;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- protocolizar documentos e requerimentos de acesso a informa&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Regulamento dispor&aacute; sobre a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e funcionamento do Servi&ccedil;o de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ao Cidad&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 10. <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&nbsp;Dever&atilde;o ser institu&iacute;dos no &acirc;mbito dos Poderes e &Oacute;rg&atilde;os de que trata o art. 5&ordm; desta Lei, N&uacute;cleos de Seguran&ccedil;a e Credenciamento - NSC, que ter&atilde;o por objetivos, promover e propor a regulamenta&ccedil;&atilde;o do credenciamento de seguran&ccedil;a de pessoas f&iacute;sicas, empresas, &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades para tratamento de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sigilosas.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Regulamento dispor&aacute; sobre a composi&ccedil;&atilde;o, organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e funcionamento do NSC, indicando procedimentos e medidas a serem adotados para o tratamento de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o sigilosa, de modo a proteg&ecirc;-la contra perda, altera&ccedil;&atilde;o indevida, acesso, transmiss&atilde;o e divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o autorizados.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">No &acirc;mbito do Poder Executivo Estadual, o N&uacute;cleo de Seguran&ccedil;a e Credenciamento &ndash; NSC, de que trata o caput, ser&aacute; coordenado pela Casa Militar.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 1cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">CAP&Iacute;TULO III</span></b></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">DA DISPONIBILIZA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O E DO ACESSO &Agrave; INFORMA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></b></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Se&ccedil;&atilde;o I</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Da Disponibiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 1cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 11.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&Eacute; dever dos Poderes, &Oacute;rg&atilde;os e Entidades albergados por esta Lei, disponibilizar, independentemente de requerimentos, no &acirc;mbito de suas compet&ecirc;ncias, informa&ccedil;&otilde;es de interesse coletivo ou geral por eles produzidas ou custodiadas.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Na disponibiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es a que se refere o caput, dever&atilde;o constar no m&iacute;nimo:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- registro das compet&ecirc;ncias e estrutura organizacional, endere&ccedil;os e telefones das respectivas unidades e hor&aacute;rios de atendimento ao p&uacute;blico;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">-&nbsp; registros de quaisquer repasses ou transfer&ecirc;ncias de recursos financeiros;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;">I<b>II</b> <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span>-&nbsp; registros das despesas;</span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- informa&ccedil;&otilde;es concernentes a procedimentos licitat&oacute;rios, inclusive os respectivos editais e resultados, bem como a todos os contratos celebrados;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">V <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- dados gerais para o acompanhamento de programas, a&ccedil;&otilde;es, projetos e obras de &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VI <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- resultados de inspe&ccedil;&otilde;es, auditorias, presta&ccedil;&otilde;es e tomadas de contas realizadas pelos &oacute;rg&atilde;os de controle interno e externo, incluindo presta&ccedil;&otilde;es de contas relativas a exerc&iacute;cios anteriores;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VII <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">-&nbsp; respostas a perguntas mais frequentes da sociedade.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Para cumprimento do disposto no caput, ser&atilde;o utilizados os seguintes meios:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- Portais da Transpar&ecirc;ncia;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- S&iacute;tios Institucionais;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- Audi&ecirc;ncias ou Consultas P&uacute;blicas.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Os instrumentos de que tratam os incisos I e II do par&aacute;grafo anterior dever&atilde;o atender, entre outros, aos seguintes requisitos:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- conter ferramenta de pesquisa de conte&uacute;do que permita o acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o de forma objetiva, transparente, clara e em linguagem de f&aacute;cil compreens&atilde;o;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- possibilitar a grava&ccedil;&atilde;o de relat&oacute;rios em diversos formatos eletr&ocirc;nicos, inclusive abertos e n&atilde;o propriet&aacute;rios, tais como planilhas e texto, de modo a facilitar a an&aacute;lise das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- possibilitar o acesso automatizado por sistemas externos em formatos abertos, estruturados e leg&iacute;veis por m&aacute;quina;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- divulgar em detalhes os formatos utilizados para estrutura&ccedil;&atilde;o da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">V <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- garantir a autenticidade e a integridade das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es dispon&iacute;veis para acesso;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VI <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- manter atualizadas as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es dispon&iacute;veis para acesso;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VII <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- indicar local e instru&ccedil;&otilde;es que permitam ao interessado comunicar-se, por via eletr&ocirc;nica ou telef&ocirc;nica, com o &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade detentora do s&iacute;tio;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VIII <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- adotar as medidas necess&aacute;rias para garantir a acessibilidade de conte&uacute;do para pessoas com defici&ecirc;ncia, nos termos do <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/LEIS/L10098.htm#art17"><span style="color: black;">art. 17 da Lei n&ordm; 10.098, de 19 de dezembro de 2000</span></a><span style="color: black;">, e do art. 9&ordm; da Conven&ccedil;&atilde;o sobre os Direitos das Pessoas com Defici&ecirc;ncia, aprovada pelo Decreto Legislativo n&ordm; 186, de 9 de julho de 2008 do Senado Federal.</span></span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;4&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">As audi&ecirc;ncias ou consultas p&uacute;blicas, de que trata o inciso III do &sect;2&ordm; do art. 11, ser&atilde;o coordenadas pela &aacute;rea de ouvidoria e a sua operacionaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o ser&aacute; objeto de regulamento pr&oacute;prio no &acirc;mbito de cada Poder e &Oacute;rg&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;5&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">As informa&ccedil;&otilde;es referentes &agrave; parcela dos recursos p&uacute;blicos recebidos pelas entidades a que se refere o art. 2&ordf; desta Lei dever&atilde;o ser disponibilizadas nos s&iacute;tios institucionais das mesmas.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 70.35pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Se&ccedil;&atilde;o II</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Do Acesso a Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 70.35pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 12. <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Qualquer interessado poder&aacute; apresentar pedido de acesso a informa&ccedil;&otilde;es aos &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades referidos no art. 1&ordm; desta Lei, devendo o pedido conter a identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o do requerente e a especifica&ccedil;&atilde;o da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o requerida.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&ordm; Os pedidos de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o dever&atilde;o ser apresentados por meio de requerimento aos Servi&ccedil;os de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ao Cidad&atilde;o ou, alternativamente, por meio dos s&iacute;tios oficiais dos &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades estaduais.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&ordm; Para o acesso a informa&ccedil;&otilde;es de interesse p&uacute;blico s&atilde;o vedadas quaisquer exig&ecirc;ncias de identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o do requerente ou dos motivos determinantes da solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o que inviabilizem o atendimento da mesma.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">No &acirc;mbito do Poder Executivo Estadual, al&eacute;m dos meios previstos no &sect;1&ordm; os pedidos de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o poder&atilde;o ser dirigidos &agrave; Central de Atendimento Telef&ocirc;nico da Ouvidoria pelo telefone 155 ou por meio do Sistema de Ouvidoria &ndash; SOU, institu&iacute;do pelo Decreto Estadual n&ordm; 30.474, de 29 de mar&ccedil;o de 2011, no endere&ccedil;o eletr&ocirc;nico </span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.ouvidoria.ce.gov.br/">www.ouvidoria.ce.gov.br</a><span style="color: black;">.</span></span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 13.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade p&uacute;blica dever&aacute; autorizar ou conceder acesso imediato &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o dispon&iacute;vel.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">N&atilde;o sendo poss&iacute;vel conceder a informa&ccedil;&atilde;o de imediato, por indisponibilidade da mesma, o Comit&ecirc; Setorial de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o do &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade que receber o pedido dever&aacute;, em prazo n&atilde;o superior a 20 (vinte) dias, remeter o requerimento ao &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade detentora da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, instruindo o requerimento com as raz&otilde;es da impossibilidade do atendimento imediato e, cientificando ao interessado.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O prazo referido no &sect; 1&ordm; poder&aacute; ser prorrogado por mais 10 (dez) dias, mediante justificativa expressa, da qual ser&aacute; cientificado o requerente.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Sem preju&iacute;zo da seguran&ccedil;a e da prote&ccedil;&atilde;o das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es e do cumprimento da legisla&ccedil;&atilde;o aplic&aacute;vel, o Servi&ccedil;o de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ao Cidad&atilde;o do &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade poder&aacute; oferecer meios para que o pr&oacute;prio requerente possa pesquisar a informa&ccedil;&atilde;o de que necessitar.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;4&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A informa&ccedil;&atilde;o armazenada em formato digital ser&aacute; fornecida nesse formato, caso haja anu&ecirc;ncia do requerente cabendo somente aos &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades propriet&aacute;rios, o fornecimento de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es hospedadas em ambientes de tecnologia da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;5&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Caso a informa&ccedil;&atilde;o solicitada esteja dispon&iacute;vel ao p&uacute;blico em formato impresso, eletr&ocirc;nico ou em qualquer outro meio de acesso universal, ser&atilde;o informados ao requerente, por escrito, o lugar e a forma pela qual se poder&aacute; consultar, obter ou reproduzir a referida informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, procedimento esse que desonerar&aacute; o &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade p&uacute;blica da obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o de seu fornecimento direto, salvo se o requerente declarar n&atilde;o dispor de meios para realizar por si mesmo tais procedimentos.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 14.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O servi&ccedil;o de busca e fornecimento da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; gratuito, salvo nas hip&oacute;teses de reprodu&ccedil;&atilde;o de documentos pelo &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade p&uacute;blica consultada, situa&ccedil;&atilde;o em que poder&aacute; ser cobrado exclusivamente o valor necess&aacute;rio ao ressarcimento do custo dos servi&ccedil;os e dos materiais utilizados, cabendo ao Comit&ecirc; Gestor instituir os valores e a forma de cobran&ccedil;a.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">. Estar&aacute; isento de ressarcir os custos previstos no caput todo aquele cuja situa&ccedil;&atilde;o econ&ocirc;mica n&atilde;o lhe permita faz&ecirc;-lo sem preju&iacute;zo do sustento pr&oacute;prio ou da fam&iacute;lia, declarada nos termos da <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/LEIS/L7115.htm"><span style="color: black;">Lei n&ordm; 7.115, de 29 de agosto de 1983</span><span style="color: purple;">.</span></a></span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 15.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Quando se tratar de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o contida em documento cuja manipula&ccedil;&atilde;o possa prejudicar sua integridade, dever&aacute; ser oferecida a consulta de c&oacute;pia, com certifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de que esta confere com o original.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Na impossibilidade de obten&ccedil;&atilde;o de c&oacute;pias, o interessado poder&aacute; solicitar que, a suas expensas e sob supervis&atilde;o de servidor p&uacute;blico, a reprodu&ccedil;&atilde;o seja feita por outro meio que n&atilde;o ponha em risco a conserva&ccedil;&atilde;o do documento original.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 16.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Quando n&atilde;o for autorizado o acesso, por se tratar de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o total ou parcialmente sigilosa, o requerente dever&aacute; ser informado sobre a possibilidade de recurso, prazos e condi&ccedil;&otilde;es para sua interposi&ccedil;&atilde;o, devendo, ainda, ser-lhe indicada a autoridade competente para sua aprecia&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">No &acirc;mbito do Poder Executivo Estadual, a <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span>negativa de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, de que trata o caput, ser&aacute; de compet&ecirc;ncia do Comit&ecirc; Setorial de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o do &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&Eacute; direito do requerente obter o inteiro teor de decis&atilde;o da negativa de acesso, por certid&atilde;o ou c&oacute;pia.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 27pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Se&ccedil;&atilde;o III</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Dos Recursos</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 71.15pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 17.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">No caso de indeferimento de acesso a informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ou &agrave;s raz&otilde;es da negativa do acesso, poder&aacute; o interessado interpor recurso contra a decis&atilde;o no prazo de 10 (dez) dias a contar da sua ci&ecirc;ncia.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O recurso ser&aacute; dirigido ao Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o do Poder ou &Oacute;rg&atilde;o correspondente, que dever&aacute; se manifestar no prazo de 5 (cinco) dias.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Verificada a proced&ecirc;ncia das raz&otilde;es do recurso, o Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o determinar&aacute; ao Comit&ecirc; Setorial de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o que adote as provid&ecirc;ncias necess&aacute;rias para dar cumprimento ao disposto nesta Lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Negado o acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o pelo Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, o requerente poder&aacute; recorrer ao Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, que deliberar&aacute; no prazo de 5 (cinco) dias se:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- o acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o classificada como sigilosa for negado;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- estiverem sendo descumpridos prazos ou outros procedimentos previstos nesta Lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;4&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Na impossibilidade de reuni&atilde;o do Comit&ecirc; Gestor ou do Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o nos prazos previstos nos &sect;&sect; 1&ordm; e 3&ordm; deste artigo, caber&aacute; respectivamente ao coordenador e ao presidente a aprecia&ccedil;&atilde;o e julgamento dos recursos.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 18.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">No caso de indeferimento de pedido de desclassifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o pelo Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, poder&aacute; o requerente recorrer ao Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, que dever&aacute; deliberar no prazo de 5 (cinco) dias.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 19.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Aplica-se subsidiariamente, no que couber, a <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/LEIS/L9784.htm"><span style="color: black;">Lei Federal n&ordm; 9.784, de 29 de janeiro de 1999</span></a><span style="color: black;">, ao procedimento de que trata este Cap&iacute;tulo.</span></span></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">CAP&Iacute;TULO IV</span></b></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">DAS RESTRI&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES DE ACESSO &Agrave; INFORMA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></b></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Se&ccedil;&atilde;o I</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Disposi&ccedil;&otilde;es Gerais</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 72pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 20.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">N&atilde;o poder&aacute; ser negado acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o necess&aacute;ria &agrave; tutela judicial ou administrativa de direitos fundamentais.</span></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">As informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ou documentos que versem sobre condutas que impliquem viola&ccedil;&atilde;o dos direitos humanos praticada por agentes p&uacute;blicos ou a mando de autoridades p&uacute;blicas n&atilde;o poder&atilde;o ser objeto de restri&ccedil;&atilde;o de acesso.</span></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 21.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O disposto nesta Lei n&atilde;o exclui as demais hip&oacute;teses legais de sigilo e de segredo de justi&ccedil;a nem as hip&oacute;teses de segredo industrial decorrentes da explora&ccedil;&atilde;o direta de atividade econ&ocirc;mica pelo Estado ou por pessoa f&iacute;sica ou entidade privada que tenha qualquer v&iacute;nculo com o poder p&uacute;blico.</span></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Se&ccedil;&atilde;o II</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Da Classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o das Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es quanto ao Grau e Prazos de Sigilo</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 22.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">S&atilde;o consideradas imprescind&iacute;veis &agrave; seguran&ccedil;a da sociedade ou do Estado e, portanto, pass&iacute;veis de classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es cuja divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o ou acesso irrestrito possam, sem preju&iacute;zo de dispositivos previstos em lei federal espec&iacute;fica:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- p&ocirc;r em risco a defesa e a soberania nacionais ou a integridade do territ&oacute;rio nacional;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- prejudicar ou p&ocirc;r em risco a condu&ccedil;&atilde;o de negocia&ccedil;&otilde;es ou as rela&ccedil;&otilde;es internacionais do Pa&iacute;s, ou as que tenham sido fornecidas em car&aacute;ter sigiloso por outros Estados e organismos internacionais;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- p&ocirc;r em risco a vida, a seguran&ccedil;a ou a sa&uacute;de da popula&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- oferecer elevado risco &agrave; estabilidade financeira, econ&ocirc;mica ou monet&aacute;ria do Pa&iacute;s;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">V <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- prejudicar ou causar risco a planos ou opera&ccedil;&otilde;es estrat&eacute;gicos de &oacute;rg&atilde;os de seguran&ccedil;a p&uacute;blica do Estado;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VI</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- prejudicar ou causar risco a projetos de pesquisa e desenvolvimento cient&iacute;fico ou tecnol&oacute;gico, assim como a sistemas, bens, instala&ccedil;&otilde;es ou &aacute;reas de interesse estrat&eacute;gico estadual;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VII</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- p&ocirc;r em risco a seguran&ccedil;a de institui&ccedil;&otilde;es ou de autoridades estaduais e seus familiares;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VIII</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- comprometer atividades de intelig&ecirc;ncia, bem como de investiga&ccedil;&atilde;o ou fiscaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o em andamento, relacionadas com a preven&ccedil;&atilde;o ou repress&atilde;o de infra&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 23.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span>informa&ccedil;&atilde;o em poder dos &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades p&uacute;blicas, observado o seu teor e em raz&atilde;o de sua imprescindibilidade &agrave; seguran&ccedil;a da sociedade ou do Estado, poder&aacute; ser classificada como ultrassecreta, secreta ou reservada.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Os prazos m&aacute;ximos de restri&ccedil;&atilde;o de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, conforme a classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o prevista no caput, vigoram a partir da data de sua produ&ccedil;&atilde;o e s&atilde;o os seguintes:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- ultrassecreta: 25 (vinte e cinco) anos;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- secreta: 15 (quinze) anos;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- reservada: 5 (cinco) anos.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">As informa&ccedil;&otilde;es que puderem colocar em risco a seguran&ccedil;a do Governador e Vice-Governador do Estado e respectivos c&ocirc;njuges e filhos(as) ser&atilde;o classificadas como reservadas e ficar&atilde;o sob sigilo at&eacute; o t&eacute;rmino do mandato em exerc&iacute;cio ou do &uacute;ltimo mandato, em caso de reelei&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Alternativamente aos prazos previstos no &sect; 1<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><sup>o</sup></span>, poder&aacute; ser estabelecida como termo final de restri&ccedil;&atilde;o de acesso &agrave; ocorr&ecirc;ncia de determinado evento, desde que este ocorra antes do transcurso do prazo m&aacute;ximo de classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;4&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Transcorrido o prazo de classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o ou consumado o evento que defina o seu termo final, a informa&ccedil;&atilde;o tornar-se-&aacute;, automaticamente, de acesso p&uacute;blico.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;5&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Para a classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o em determinado grau de sigilo, dever&aacute; ser observado o interesse p&uacute;blico da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o e utilizado o crit&eacute;rio menos restritivo poss&iacute;vel, considerados:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- a gravidade do risco ou dano &agrave; seguran&ccedil;a da sociedade e do Estado;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- o prazo m&aacute;ximo de restri&ccedil;&atilde;o de acesso ou o evento que defina seu termo final.</span></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Se&ccedil;&atilde;o III</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Da Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o e do Controle de Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es Sigilosas</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 71.15pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 24.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&Eacute; dever do Estado controlar o acesso e a divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sigilosas produzidas por seus &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades, assegurando a sua prote&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O acesso, a divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o e o tratamento de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o classificada como sigilosa ficar&atilde;o restritos a pessoas que tenham necessidade de conhec&ecirc;-la e que sejam devidamente credenciadas nos termos do art. 10 desta Lei, sem preju&iacute;zo das atribui&ccedil;&otilde;es dos agentes p&uacute;blicos autorizados por lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o classificada como sigilosa cria a obriga&ccedil;&atilde;o para aquele que a obteve de resguardar o sigilo.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 25.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">As autoridades p&uacute;blicas adotar&atilde;o as provid&ecirc;ncias necess&aacute;rias para que o pessoal a elas subordinado hierarquicamente conhe&ccedil;a as normas e observe as medidas e procedimentos de seguran&ccedil;a para tratamento de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sigilosas.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A pessoa f&iacute;sica ou entidade privada que, em raz&atilde;o de qualquer v&iacute;nculo com o poder p&uacute;blico, executar atividades de tratamento de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sigilosas adotar&aacute; as provid&ecirc;ncias necess&aacute;rias para que seus empregados, prepostos ou representantes observem as medidas e procedimentos de seguran&ccedil;a das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es resultantes da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o desta Lei.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 2cm; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Se&ccedil;&atilde;o IV</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Dos Procedimentos de Classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o, Reclassifica&ccedil;&atilde;o e Desclassifica&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 26.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span>classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o do grau de sigilo de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es como ultrassecreto, secreto e reservado ficar&aacute; a cargo dos Comit&ecirc;s Gestores de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos Poderes e &Oacute;rg&atilde;os referidos no art. 5&ordm; desta Lei.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico. <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o dever&aacute; encaminhar ao Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o as decis&otilde;es que classificarem informa&ccedil;&otilde;es como ultrassecretas.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 27.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span>classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o em qualquer grau de sigilo dever&aacute; ser formalizada em decis&atilde;o que conter&aacute;, no m&iacute;nimo, os seguintes elementos:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- assunto sobre o qual versa a informa&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- fundamento da classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o, observados os crit&eacute;rios estabelecidos no art. 22;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- indica&ccedil;&atilde;o do prazo de sigilo, contado em anos, meses ou dias, ou do evento que defina o seu termo final, conforme limites previstos no art. 23;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o dos respons&aacute;veis pela classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A decis&atilde;o referida no caput ser&aacute; mantida no mesmo grau de sigilo da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o classificada.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 28.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span>classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es ser&aacute; reavaliada pelo Comit&ecirc; Gestor de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o ou pelo Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, mediante provoca&ccedil;&atilde;o ou de of&iacute;cio, nos termos previstos em regulamento, com vistas &agrave; sua desclassifica&ccedil;&atilde;o ou &agrave; redu&ccedil;&atilde;o do prazo de sigilo, observado o disposto nos arts. 22 e 23.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O regulamento a que se refere o caput dever&aacute; considerar as peculiaridades das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es produzidas no exterior por autoridades ou agentes p&uacute;blicos.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Na reavalia&ccedil;&atilde;o a que se refere o caput, dever&atilde;o ser examinadas a perman&ecirc;ncia dos motivos do sigilo e a possibilidade de danos decorrentes do acesso ou da divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Na hip&oacute;tese de redu&ccedil;&atilde;o do prazo de sigilo da informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, o novo prazo de restri&ccedil;&atilde;o manter&aacute; como termo inicial a data da sua produ&ccedil;&atilde;o.&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 29</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">. O Comit&ecirc; Setorial de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o publicar&aacute;, anualmente, nos s&iacute;tios institucionais de cada &oacute;rg&atilde;o e entidade, a veicula&ccedil;&atilde;o dos seguintes dados:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- rol das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es que tenham sido desclassificadas nos &uacute;ltimos 12 (doze) meses;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- rol de documentos classificados em cada grau de sigilo, com identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o para refer&ecirc;ncia futura;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- relat&oacute;rio estat&iacute;stico contendo a quantidade de pedidos de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o recebidos, atendidos e indeferidos, bem como informa&ccedil;&otilde;es gen&eacute;ricas sobre os solicitantes.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Os &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades dever&atilde;o manter exemplar da publica&ccedil;&atilde;o prevista no caput para consulta p&uacute;blica em suas sedes.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Os &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades manter&atilde;o extrato com a lista de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es classificadas, acompanhadas da data, do grau de sigilo e dos fundamentos da classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 72pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Se&ccedil;&atilde;o V</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Das Informa&ccedil;&otilde;es Pessoais</span></b></span></p>
<p class="seo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 30.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O tratamento das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es pessoais deve ser feito de forma transparente e com respeito &agrave; intimidade, vida privada, honra e imagem das pessoas, bem como &agrave;s liberdades e garantias individuais.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">As informa&ccedil;&otilde;es pessoais, a que se refere este artigo, relativas &agrave; intimidade, vida privada, honra e imagem:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- ter&atilde;o seu acesso restrito, independentemente de classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de sigilo e pelo prazo m&aacute;ximo de 100 (cem) anos a contar da sua data de produ&ccedil;&atilde;o, a agentes p&uacute;blicos legalmente autorizados e &agrave; pessoa a que elas se referirem;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- poder&atilde;o ter autorizada sua divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o ou acesso por terceiros diante de previs&atilde;o legal ou consentimento expresso da pessoa a que elas se referirem.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Aquele que obtiver acesso &agrave;s informa&ccedil;&otilde;es, de que trata este artigo, ser&aacute; responsabilizado por seu uso indevido.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O consentimento referido no inciso II do &sect; 1&ordm; n&atilde;o ser&aacute; exigido quando as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es forem necess&aacute;rias:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- &agrave; preven&ccedil;&atilde;o e diagn&oacute;stico m&eacute;dico, quando a pessoa estiver f&iacute;sica ou legalmente incapaz, e para utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o &uacute;nica e exclusivamente para o tratamento m&eacute;dico;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- &agrave; realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de estat&iacute;sticas e pesquisas cient&iacute;ficas de evidente interesse p&uacute;blico ou geral, previstos em lei, sendo vedada a identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o da pessoa a que as informa&ccedil;&otilde;es se referirem;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- ao cumprimento de ordem judicial;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- &agrave; defesa de direitos humanos;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">V <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- &agrave; prote&ccedil;&atilde;o do interesse p&uacute;blico e geral preponderante.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;4</span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&ordm; A restri&ccedil;&atilde;o de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o relativa &agrave; vida privada, honra e imagem de pessoa n&atilde;o poder&aacute; ser invocada com o intuito de prejudicar processo de apura&ccedil;&atilde;o de irregularidades em que o titular das informa&ccedil;&otilde;es estiver envolvido, bem como em a&ccedil;&otilde;es voltadas para a recupera&ccedil;&atilde;o de fatos hist&oacute;ricos de maior relev&acirc;ncia.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;5&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Regulamento dispor&aacute; sobre os procedimentos para tratamento de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o pessoal.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">CAP&Iacute;TULO V</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">DAS RESPONSABILIDADES</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 31.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Constituem condutas il&iacute;citas que ensejam responsabilidade do agente p&uacute;blico ou militar:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- recusar-se a fornecer informa&ccedil;&atilde;o requerida nos termos desta Lei, retardar deliberadamente o seu fornecimento ou fornec&ecirc;-la intencionalmente de forma incorreta, incompleta ou imprecisa;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- utilizar indevidamente, bem como subtrair, destruir, inutilizar, desfigurar, alterar ou ocultar, total ou parcialmente, informa&ccedil;&atilde;o que se encontre sob sua guarda ou a que tenha acesso ou conhecimento em raz&atilde;o do exerc&iacute;cio das atribui&ccedil;&otilde;es de cargo, emprego ou fun&ccedil;&atilde;o p&uacute;blica;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- agir com dolo ou m&aacute;-f&eacute; na an&aacute;lise das solicita&ccedil;&otilde;es de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- divulgar ou permitir a divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o ou acessar ou permitir acesso indevido &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o sigilosa ou informa&ccedil;&atilde;o pessoal;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">V</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- impor sigilo &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o para obter proveito pessoal ou de terceiro, ou para fins de oculta&ccedil;&atilde;o de ato ilegal cometido por si ou por outrem;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VI</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- ocultar da revis&atilde;o de autoridade superior competente informa&ccedil;&atilde;o sigilosa para beneficiar a si ou a outrem, ou em preju&iacute;zo de terceiros;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">VII</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- destruir ou subtrair, por qualquer meio, documentos concernentes a poss&iacute;veis viola&ccedil;&otilde;es de direitos humanos por parte de agentes do Estado.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Atendido o princ&iacute;pio do contradit&oacute;rio, da ampla defesa e do devido processo legal, as condutas descritas no caput ser&atilde;o consideradas:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- para fins dos regulamentos disciplinares dos Militares, transgress&otilde;es m&eacute;dias ou graves, segundo os crit&eacute;rios neles estabelecidos, desde que n&atilde;o tipificadas em lei como crime ou contraven&ccedil;&atilde;o penal;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- para fins do disposto na <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/LEIS/L8112cons.htm"><span style="color: black;">Lei n&ordm; 9.826, de 14 de maio de 19</span></a><span style="color: black;">74, e suas altera&ccedil;&otilde;es, infra&ccedil;&otilde;es administrativas, que dever&atilde;o ser apenadas, no m&iacute;nimo, com suspens&atilde;o, segundo os crit&eacute;rios nela estabelecidos.</span></span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm; <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Pelas condutas descritas no caput, poder&aacute; o militar ou agente p&uacute;blico responder, tamb&eacute;m, por improbidade administrativa, conforme o disposto nas <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/LEIS/l1079consol.htm"><span style="color: black;">Leis n&ordm;s. 1.079, de 10 de abril de 1950</span></a><span style="color: black;">, e <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span><a href="http://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/LEIS/L8429.htm"><span style="color: black;">8.429, de 2 de junho de 1992.</span></a></span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 32.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span>pessoa f&iacute;sica ou entidade privada que detiver informa&ccedil;&otilde;es em virtude de v&iacute;nculo de qualquer natureza com o poder p&uacute;blico e deixar de observar o disposto nesta Lei estar&aacute; sujeita &agrave;s seguintes san&ccedil;&otilde;es:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- advert&ecirc;ncia;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- multa;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- rescis&atilde;o do v&iacute;nculo com o poder p&uacute;blico;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">IV <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- suspens&atilde;o tempor&aacute;ria de participar em licita&ccedil;&atilde;o e impedimento de contratar com a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica por prazo n&atilde;o superior a 2 (dois) anos;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">V</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- declara&ccedil;&atilde;o de inidoneidade para licitar ou contratar com a Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica, at&eacute; que seja promovida a reabilita&ccedil;&atilde;o perante a pr&oacute;pria autoridade que aplicou a penalidade.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;1&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">As san&ccedil;&otilde;es previstas nos incisos I, III e IV poder&atilde;o ser aplicadas juntamente com a do inciso II, assegurado o direito de defesa do interessado, no respectivo processo, no prazo de 10 (dez) dias.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;2&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A reabilita&ccedil;&atilde;o referida no inciso V ser&aacute; autorizada somente quando o interessado efetivar o ressarcimento ao &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade dos preju&iacute;zos resultantes e ap&oacute;s decorrido o prazo da san&ccedil;&atilde;o aplicada com base no inciso IV.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">&sect;3&ordm;</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">A aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o da san&ccedil;&atilde;o prevista no inciso V &eacute; de compet&ecirc;ncia exclusiva da autoridade m&aacute;xima do &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade p&uacute;blica, facultada a defesa do interessado, no respectivo processo, no prazo de 10 (dez) dias da abertura de vista.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 33.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Os &oacute;rg&atilde;os e entidades p&uacute;blicas respondem diretamente pelos danos causados em decorr&ecirc;ncia da divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o autorizada ou utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o indevida de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es sigilosas ou informa&ccedil;&otilde;es pessoais, cabendo a apura&ccedil;&atilde;o de responsabilidade funcional nos casos de dolo ou culpa, assegurado o respectivo direito de regresso.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico. <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O disposto neste artigo aplica-se &agrave; pessoa f&iacute;sica ou entidade privada que, em virtude de v&iacute;nculo de qualquer natureza com &oacute;rg&atilde;os ou entidades, tenha acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o sigilosa ou pessoal e a submeta a tratamento indevido.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-indent: 72pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">CAP&Iacute;TULO VI</span></b></span></p>
<p class="cap" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">DISPOSI&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES FINAIS E TRANSIT&Oacute;RIAS</span></b></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 34.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Aplica-se, no que couber, a <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><a href="https://www.planalto.gov.br/ccivil_03/LEIS/L9507.htm"><span style="color: black;">Lei Federal n&ordm; 9.507, de 12 de novembro de 1997</span></a><span style="color: black;">, em rela&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o de pessoa, f&iacute;sica ou jur&iacute;dica, constante de registro ou banco de dados de entidades governamentais ou de car&aacute;ter p&uacute;blico.</span></span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 35. <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">No prazo de 30 (trinta) dias, a contar da vig&ecirc;ncia desta Lei, ser&aacute; providenciado:</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- designa&ccedil;&atilde;o por ato pr&oacute;prio dos Chefes de Poder e &Oacute;rg&atilde;o, previstos no art. 5&ordm; desta Lei, de autoridade que lhe seja diretamente subordinada, para represent&aacute;-lo no Conselho Estadual de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- defini&ccedil;&atilde;o da composi&ccedil;&atilde;o e designa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos representantes que ir&atilde;o integrar os Comit&ecirc;s Gestores de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, no &acirc;mbito dos Poderes e &Oacute;rg&atilde;os citados no art. 5&ordm; desta Lei;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- <b><span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></b></span>designa&ccedil;&atilde;o por ato formal do dirigente m&aacute;ximo de cada &oacute;rg&atilde;o ou entidade do Poder Executivo Estadual, dos representantes do Comit&ecirc; Setorial de Acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, segundo o estabelecido no art. 8&ordm; desta Lei.</span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 36. <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">O Conselho Estadual de acesso &agrave; Informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, promover&aacute;:&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">I <span style="font-family: Arial;"></span></span></b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- campanha de fomento &agrave; cultura da transpar&ecirc;ncia na Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica e conscientiza&ccedil;&atilde;o do direito fundamental de acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">II</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- treinamento de agentes p&uacute;blicos no que se refere ao desenvolvimento de pr&aacute;ticas relacionadas &agrave; transpar&ecirc;ncia na Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica;</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">III</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">- monitoramento da aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o da lei no &acirc;mbito da Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o P&uacute;blica Estadual,&nbsp; consolidando a publica&ccedil;&atilde;o de informa&ccedil;&otilde;es estat&iacute;sticas de que trata o art. 29.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Art. 37.</span></b> <span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;"></span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black;">Os Chefes dos Poderes e &Oacute;rg&atilde;os citados no art. 5&ordm; desta Lei, expedir&atilde;o, no prazo m&aacute;ximo de 180 (cento e oitenta) dias, a contar da sua vig&ecirc;ncia os regulamentos nela previstos.</span></span></p>
<p class="artigo" style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-size: 12pt;"></span></p>
